## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some sources may not have been accessible due to publication restrictions or paywalls. Additionally, the complexity of global supply chains and regional variations in consumer behavior may not be fully captured in this analysis. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the nuanced impacts of consumerism on the environment.